  "prompt": "What should I do to tell her I love you?",
  "response": "Expressing your feelings can be a meaningful moment. Here are some steps to consider:\n\n1. **Choose the Right Moment**: Find a time when you can both relax and talk without distractions.\n\n2. **Be Genuine**: Speak from the heart and be authentic about your feelings.\n\n3. **Consider Your Approach**: You could say it directly (\"I love you\") or share what you appreciate about her and how she makes you feel.\n\n4. **Create a Comfortable Atmosphere**: Set the mood, maybe during a special outing, a cozy evening at home, or over a nice dinner.\n\n5. **Be Prepared for Any Response**: Understand that she may not feel the same way immediately, and that\u2019s okay. Give her space to process.\n\n6. **Follow Up with Actions**: Show your love through kind gestures and support. Actions can reinforce your words.\n\nWhatever you decide to do, make sure it reflects your true feelings!",
